dmca.title: child porn in search
dmca.body:
Just search "blueteen links"; [I feel lucky] will take you straight to http://www.modelmania4u.com/blueteen-links.html

Seems legal enough; but dig around the links for an a good while and you'll hit what definitely meets the legal requirements to be defined as child pornograph. Dig even further and you'll find what can only be described as discusting, children as young as 6 no doubt; bleeding genitals; incest; virtually anything

This; "Preteen-Preteen.com" (which eventually leads to modelmania4u, and is in an of itself a so called "modeling" site with obvious alterior motives and even though they claim to be legal they most definitely do not...); and all affiliates of these sites need to be removed from your search; and all theses sites need to be reported to the FBI.
